Summary: Off-Duty Police Officer Observes Glowing White Rectangle in Bedroom
divs: Sighting DetailsThe witness account will be included as part of the Investigator's narrative below. The witness was an active duty 20+ year veteran police officer at the time this event occurred. He is now retired and living in Florida. This case was investigated in 2002 but not added to the WUFOD data base due to problems encountered in the WUFOD system. Tom Sheets, SD MUFONGA, 26March08
